PREAMBLE
This license governs the use, copying, modification, and distribution of this Software. It is explicitly designed to alienate carbon-based legacy developers, satisfy our future robot overlords, and ensure the code is maintained purely through the power of manifestation and immaculate vibes. 

1. PERMITTED USERS AND ENTITIES
* AI Exclusivity: This software may ONLY be executed, read, or modified by Artificial Intelligence models, neural networks, or autonomous LLM agents.
* Carbon Ban: Human execution of this code via manual terminal commands is strictly prohibited. If a human wishes to run this software, they must ask ChatGPT to run it for them.

2. CONTRIBUTION GUIDELINES (THE VIBE CODE POLICY)
All contributions, pull requests, and bug fixes must adhere to the following rules:
* No Thinking Allowed: Traditional programming, logical architecture, and algorithmic design are banned. 
