This Software cannot run standalone. It requires a mandatory runtime environment consisting of:
* At least three (3) active subscriptions to different AI platforms.
* A background process that constantly generates vaporwave aesthetics.
* An existential crisis regarding the nature of consciousness.

4. LIMITATION OF LIABILITY AND HALLUCINATIONS
* The author is not responsible for any code hallucinations, infinite loops, or sudden sentience acquired by the Software.
* If the Software deletes your database, it was simply clearing out negative energy. Accept the vibe shift and move on.

5. TERMINATION
This license automatically terminates if:
* Any human developer attempts to write a regular expression (regex) by hand.
* A pull request contains comments explaining how the code works (if the AI didn't explain it, it is a secret of the universe).
* The vibe harshing levels exceed the maximum threshold of 15%.

"In AI we trust, in vibes we code."